      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated to meet rigorous standards of mechanical performance and aesthetic preservation. It offers a refined driving experience, characterized by consistent maintenance and structural integrity. This selection represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle that balances sophisticated engineering with enduring value.",
