      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! It runs super smooth and looks great too. If you're looking for a dependable ride that won't let you down, come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 33800.0,
