    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a purist\u2019s specimen, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline, transferred through a 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure peak mechanical synchronization. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with updated bushings for precise turn-in and reduced deflection. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the chassis remains rigid and the compression across all six cylinders is within factory tolerances. This is a mechanically sorted driver's car ready for the apex.",
